com.gilran.chess.server

Class ServiceImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gilran.chess.server.ServiceImpl

  • public class ServiceImpl
extends java.lang.Object
    The chess service implementation.

    Each public method in this class is mapped to the corresponding path of the web service. The RequestHandler uses reflection in order to choose the method.

    Due to this, each public method must have a Status return value and take exactly 2 params, where the first is a proto message and the second is a Callback.

    Author:
    Gil Ran
